Hello, <%= user_email.user.full_name %>!

You have requested to reset your password. To do that, copy and paste the following URL into your browser's address bar and press Enter, then you will be presented with a page where you can set the password to a new one.

http://<%= config.hostname! %>/user/reset_password?email=<%= user_email.email %>&token=<%= authentication.password_reset_token %>
